{"name": "kindle-to-markdown", "metadata": {"name": "kindle-to-markdown", "version": "0.0.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "License :: Other/Proprietary License", "Natural Language :: English", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": "Apache 2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["beautifulsoup4", "click", "twine"], "summary": "A simple program to convert Kindle HTML annotations to a Markdown file.", "upload_time": 1735389370}, "documentation": ["# Kindle Annotations to Markdown\n\n> A simple program to convert Kindle HTML annotations to a Markdown file\n\n## Features\n\n-   Conversion of page bookmarks, text highlights, and notes to Markdown\n-   Included reference positions of annotations\n-   Automatic detection of annotation file's language ([currently supported](kindle_to_markdown/languages.py))\n\n## Usage\n\n```shell\n$ kindle_to_markdown --help\nUsage: kindle_to_markdown [OPTIONS]\n\n  A simple program to convert Kindle HTML annotations to a Markdown file.\n\nOptions:\n  -i, --input-file PATH   Path to the Kindle annotations HTML file.\n                          [required]\n  -o, --output-file PATH  Path to the Markdown file.\n  -p, --print-only        Only print Markdown to the console.\n  --help                  Show this message and exit.\n```\n\n## Installation\n\n### From PyPi\n\n```shell\npip install kindle-to-markdown\n```\n\n### From Source\n\nPrerequisites:\n\n-   `python` in a [supported version](pyproject.toml) available on your path.\n-   Package manager `poetry` installed (e.g., `python -m pip install poetry`)\n\n```shell\nmake\npoetry run python -m kindle_to_markdown --help\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "kindle_to_markdown", "documentation": ["Module init-file.", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "kindle_to_markdown.languages", "documentation": ["Language definitions for Kindle annotation file.", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "kindle_to_markdown.languages.SUPPORTED_LANGUAGES", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "kindle_to_markdown.__main__", "documentation": ["Module main-file.", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [{"name": "kindle_to_markdown.__main__.extract_note_heading", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "el_text", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "trsl", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "NoteHeading", "xref": {"fqname": "NoteHeading", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kindle_to_markdown.__main__.__clean_text", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "el_text", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "kindle_to_markdown.__main__.extract_annotations", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "soup", "type": {"name": "BeautifulSoup", "xref": {"fqname": "bs4.BeautifulSoup", "project": "beautifulsoup4"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "trsl", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "